[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="BreachBand" load_steps=3 format=3]

; Arc-4 Round 24 reframe (iter 284 per user-direction iter 283 Option B):
; Q1 breach-economy proof room. Standalone BreachBand designed to prove
; the consult-001 Q1 finding (conf 0.90): "shells are route currency, not
; just damage flavor." 4 distinct vertical lanes, each gated by a
; different shell class. The layout itself lives in
; loop/breach/q1_proof_layout.txt (ASCII grid). This resource carries
; the band-level metadata (name + dominant pressure + canonical answer)
; and a tuned LevelConfig that nudges procedural generation toward the
; 4-lane structure when the layout file is not consumed directly.

